name: NFT Consultation Ticket
description:
As a thank you to my Twitter followers for reaching the 2,000 follower level. 

I was wanting to do something to give back to the community and thought this ticket for a free 15 minute consultation might be useful to some new, or struggling artist or collectors... or maybe to people just looking at new ideas.

I wish I could do it 100% free, but then the bots would grab them all. I know I have a few bots stalking my drops thee days.  

Again this is not legal or financial advice, just my thoughts and suggestion to try or not to try if they work for you.  After your appointment you may sell or pass on the NFT to someone else and I will honor for each holder until June.
